"1  (7- to 9-pound) bone-in spiral ham","2 tablespoons butter","1  shallot, minced","1/2 cup pure maple syrup","1/4 cup dark brown sugar","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","2 teaspoons balsamic vinegar","1/4 teaspoon cracked black pepper","  Garnishes: orange wedges, fresh rosemary sprigs"